modelVersions.name: ichinomiyayuu-v1-8k
modelVersions.description:
Used a different training setting (beta schedule = linear), same as the kurige model.

This setting seems better at colors, shapes/composition, but more biased towards a painterly style.

Trained more than the 4k version.
